Achievements.Name: Newcomer
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have joined a team.

Achievements.Name: Assembler
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have assembled an AC.

Achievements.Name: Coordinator
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have colored an AC.

Achievements.Name: Artist
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have edited an emblem.

Achievements.Name: Three Forces
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have joined a team affiliated with one of the Three Forces.

Achievements.Name: Normal Sortie
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have gone on a normal sortie.

Achievements.Name: Normal Sortie Victory
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have been victorious on a normal sortie.

Achievements.Name: Special Sortie
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have gone on a special sortie.

Achievements.Name: Special Sortie Victory
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have been victorious on a special sortie.

Achievements.Name: Medalist
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have earned any medal on a sortie in World Mode.

Achievements.Name: Squadron Sortie
Achievements.Description: Given when a normal or special sortie of 4 or more occurs. (Mercenaries or UNACs count as 1 player.)

Achievements.Name: Architect
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have created a UNAC by customizing its operations.

Achievements.Name: Operator
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have joined a normal or special sortie as an operator and been victorious.

Achievements.Name: UNAC Operations
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have served as operator on a squad that includes a UNAC and been victorious.

Achievements.Name: Custom Territory
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have customized their territory.

Achievements.Name: Signs
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have accepted a contract as a mercenary and gone on a sortie.

Achievements.Name: Contract Completed
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have accepted and successfully completed a contract as a mercenary.

Achievements.Name: War Reporter
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have taken a screenshot.

Achievements.Name: First Down
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have battled against an AC and destroyed it.

Achievements.Name: Player Rank E
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have attained a player rank of E or higher.

Achievements.Name: Player Rank S
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have attained a player rank of S.

Achievements.Name: Team Rank E
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have been a member of a team ranked E or higher.

Achievements.Name: Team Rank A
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have been a member of a team ranked A or higher.

Achievements.Name: Mission: 01 Clear
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have cleared Story Mission: 01 Dirty Worker.

Achievements.Name: Mission: 02 Clear
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have cleared Story Mission: 02 Trickster.

Achievements.Name: Mission: 03 Clear
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have cleared Story Mission: 03 Rusting Steel.

Achievements.Name: Mission: 04 Clear
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have cleared Story Mission: 04 Peekaboo.

Achievements.Name: Mission: 05 Clear
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have cleared Story Mission: 05 Secret Game.

Achievements.Name: Mission: 06 Clear
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have cleared Story Mission: 06 Blue Magnolia.

Achievements.Name: Mission: 07 Clear
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have cleared Story Mission: 07 Gravity.

Achievements.Name: Mission: 08 Clear
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have cleared Story Mission: 08 Vendetta.

Achievements.Name: Mission: 09 Clear
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have cleared Story Mission: 09 Forgiveness for an Angel.

Achievements.Name: Mission: 10 Clear
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have cleared Story Mission: 10 Mechanized Memories.

Achievements.Name: Story Missions Clear
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have cleared all Story Missions.

Achievements.Name: Intel Gatherer
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have viewed the news under Player Information.

Achievements.Name: Parts Master
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have acquired all AC parts.

Achievements.Name: Emblem Master
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have acquired all emblems/pieces from the shop, enemy ACs.

Achievements.Name: Architect Master
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have maxed out all grades through UNAC expansion.

Achievements.Name: Operator Master
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have served as operator on an all-UNAC squad and been victorious.

Achievements.Name: Territory Master
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have purchased all defense systems and formations for territory customization.

Achievements.Name: Story Master
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have cleared every Story Mission with rank S.

Achievements.Name: Subquest Master
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have completed every Story Mission subquest.

Achievements.Name: Berserker
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have cleared Story Mission Hardcore Mode (any type).

Achievements.Name: Ruins King
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have destroyed Scavenger, Hunter, and Predator in World Mode.

Achievements.Name: Wasteland King
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have destroyed To-605A, To-605S, and To-605D in World Mode.

Achievements.Name: Contamination King
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have destroyed Grey Lotus in World Mode.

Achievements.Name: Marsh King
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have destroyed the Spirit Class Moving Fortress in World Mode.

Achievements.Name: Frost King
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have destroyed Exusia in World Mode.

Achievements.Name: Polar King
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have destroyed LiV in World Mode.

Achievements.Name: Desert King
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those who have destroyed N-WGIX/v in World Mode.
